      </section>
      <example>
         <p>The %display-atts; parameter entity is used within the DITA dtds
as a common definition for attributes that affect presentation of certain
elements. Not all of these capabilities have been provided yet for DITA topic
processing. A typical example might be:</p>
         <codeblock>&lt;codeblock scale="90" frame="topbot" expanse="page"&gt;
/* a long sample program */
Do forever
  Say "Hello, World"
End
&lt;/codeblock&gt;</codeblock>
      </example>
